OL,7,FThe parents of Madeleine McCann are
OL,8,Famong 30 people who have written to
OL,9,Fthe prime minister calling for greater
OL,10,Fscrutiny of the UK media.
OL,12,FGerry McCann said his family were
OL,13,Fsubjected to "monstering" by sections
OL,14,Fof the press and are lucky to have
OL,15,F"survived".
OL,17,FHe also said that parts of the UK
OL,18,Fmedia made him feel as though he was
OL,19,Fbeing "suffocated and buried" after
OL,20,Fhis daughter disappeared.
