OL,7,FOther signatories of the letter who
OL,8,Fwrote to Sir Keir Starmer include
OL,9,Ffamilies of Hillsborough and 7/7
OL,10,Fbombing victims and the mother of TV
OL,11,Fpresenter Caroline Flack. They are
OL,12,Furging the government to reverse its
OL,13,Fdecision not to hold the second phase
OL,14,Fof the Leveson Inquiry.
OL,16,FThe inquiry examined the culture,
OL,17,Fpractices and ethics of the British
OL,18,Fpress following the News International
OL,19,Fphone-hacking scandal.
