OL,7,FThe abandoned second phase would have
OL,8,Flooked at unlawful behaviour by parts
OL,9,Fof the media, as well as the
OL,10,Frelationships between journalists,
OL,11,Fpoliticians and the police.
OL,13,FMcCann, 57, told BBC Radio 4's Today
OL,14,Fprogramme on Wednesday that, more than
OL,15,Fa year after Labour came to power,
OL,16,F"press regulation is no longer a
OL,17,Fpriority".
