OL,7,FHe added that he is "extremely
OL,8,Fdisappointed" that the party has not
OL,9,Fcommitted to implementing some of the
OL,10,Frecommendations from the first part of
OL,11,Fthe Leveson Inquiry, despite
OL,12,Fsupporting them before the election.
OL,14,F"We're over a year into the
OL,15,Fgovernment, and there haven't been any
OL,16,Fchanges," he said.
OL,18,F"It's not acceptable to me now, more
OL,19,Fthan a year on, that Leveson and press
OL,20,Fregulation is no longer a priority."
