OL,7,FCulture Secretary Lisa Nandy told ITV
OL,8,FNews on Wednesday that she is willing
OL,9,Fto meet Gerry McCann and others
OL,10,Faffected by press abuse to discuss
OL,11,Fpossible future government action.
OL,13,FNandy said she has ruled out a second
OL,14,Fphase of the Leveson Inquiry, but
OL,15,Fadded that this does not mean the
OL,16,Fgovernment will not take further action
OL,18,F"We took a position before the general
OL,19,Felection that pursuing Leveson 2 in
OL,20,Fits entirety would not be the right
OL,21,Fapproach," she said.
