OL,7,F"The reason for that is that we've got
OL,8,Fa really dissatisfactory situation in
OL,9,Fthis country, where broadcast media
OL,10,Fare held to one set of standards, the
OL,11,Fpress are held to another, and the
OL,12,Fonline world is held to a different
OL,13,Fset of standards altogether.
OL,15,F"And what that means is that there
OL,16,Fisn't enough protection for
OL,17,Findividuals who are, like Gerry
OL,18,FMcCann, suffering from appalling
OL,19,Fpractices and intrusion that can ruin
OL,20,Ftheir lives.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
