OL,7,F"It also means that we've got to think
OL,8,Fcarefully about how we balance the
OL,9,Frights of victims with the need to
OL,10,Fhave a free press that has always been
OL,11,Fresponsible for regulating itself in
OL,12,Forder that it can hold the powerful,
OL,13,Fincluding people like me, to account."
OL,15,FIn his interview, Mr McCann also said
OL,16,Fthe headlines, hounding and abuse from
OL,17,Fthe media can have a devastating
OL,18,Fimpact on people's lives, adding that
OL,19,Fpress coverage of Madeleine's
OL,20,Fdisappearance in 2007 took a "huge
OL,21,Ftoll" on his family.
