OL,7,F"Obviously, we had sustained interest
OL,8,Fand misleading headlines for 15 months
OL,9,For more that forced us, forced us to
OL,10,Ftake legal action to stop it," he said.
OL,12,F"But no one, no one wants to go to
OL,13,Fcourt."
OL,15,FHe added: "We had tremendous support.
OL,17,F"But I can promise you, there were
OL,18,Ftimes where I felt like I was
OL,19,Fdrowning, and it was the media,
OL,20,Fprimarily.
