OL,7,F"It was what was happening and the way
OL,8,Fthings were being portrayed, where you
OL,9,Fwere being suffocated and buried, and
OL,10,Fit felt like there wasn't a way out."
OL,12,FMr McCann said the press "repeatedly
OL,13,Finterfered" with the investigation
OL,14,Finto Madeleine's disappearance.
OL,16,FHe said that for months afterwards,
OL,17,Fjournalists came to the family's home
OL,18,Fand photographers were "literally
OL,19,Framming their cameras against" their
OL,20,Fcar window, terrifying the couple's
OL,21,Ftwo-year-old twins.
