OL,8,Fbeen confidential, should be passed on
OL,9,Fto the police, witness statements,
OL,10,Fmany other things that have gone out,"
OL,11,Fhe added.
OL,13,F"So if you were the perpetrator, you
OL,14,Fknew a lot more than you should have
OL,15,Fdone ` and as a victim, as a parent,
OL,16,Fit's absolutely dismaying."
